    </h2>
    <div class="content__carousel">
        <div class="slide slide--responsive">
            <div class="slide__into" tabindex="0" id="use-slider">
              <div class="content__item slide__item">
                <figure>
                  <picture>
                    <img src="{{ 'great1.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="270" height="160">
                  </picture>
                  <figcaption>
                    <b>Serpentine Design</b>
                    Allows Magic Tracks® to bend, flex, and curve in any direction
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </div>
              <div class="content__item slide__item">
                <figure>
                  <picture>
                    <img src="{{ 'great2.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="270" height="160">
                  </picture>
                  <figcaption>
                    <b>GLOW IN THE DARK</b>
                    The track's neon colors shine super bright
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </div>
              <div class="content__item slide__item">
                <figure>
                  <picture>
                    <img src="{{ 'great3.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="270" height="160">
                  </picture>
                  <figcaption>
                    <b>LED LIGHTS</b>
                    Race car's 5 LED lights keep the track glowing as it keeps going
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </div>
              <div class="content__item slide__item">
                <figure>
                  <picture>
                    <img src="{{ 'great4.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="270" height="160">
                  </picture>
                  <figcaption>
                    <b>PIECES SNAP TOGETHER</b>
                    Build a custom speedway in seconds
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </div>
              <div class="content__item slide__item">
                <figure>
                  <picture>
                    <img src="{{ 'great5.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="270" height="160">
                  </picture>
                  <figcaption>
                    <b>TRACK ROLLS UP</b>
                    For quick and easy storage
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </div>
              <div class="content__item slide__item">
                <figure>
                  <picture>
                    <img src="{{ 'great6.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="270" height="160">
                  </picture>
                  <figcaption>
                    <b>ENDLESS FUN</b>
                    You'll never have the same race twice
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slide__nav">
              <button aria-label="Previous" class="slide__prev" type="button">
                <svg class="icon">
                  <use href="#icon-chevron"></use>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <button aria-label="Next" class="slide__next" type="button">
                <svg class="icon">
                  <use href="#icon-chevron"></use>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section aria-labelledby="intro-title" class="view content content--picture-text section">
  <div id="intro" class="view__anchor"></div>
  <div class="view__in section__in">
    <div class="section__block">
      <div class="content__group">
        <div class="content__text">
          <h2 id="intro-title" class="content__title">
            Bend it, Curve it to the Max!
          </h2>
          <p>
            <b>{{ shop.name }}</b> are the totally new cool race tracks that bend and glow like you've never seen before. You can bend, flex, and curve the track magically in 360˚ however you want – even while the race car is zooming around.
          </p>
          <p>
            Just snap the pieces together and you get a fully customized speedway of your own creation. And even better, when you turn off the light, <b>{{ shop.name }}</b> glows super bright!
          </p>
          <div class="content__footer">
            <a
              href="#order"
              class="dtm-button"
              >
                <span>Order Now</span>
              </a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <picture class="content__picture">
          <img src="{{ 'magic-tracks-car.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="390" height="245" loading="lazy">
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<svg hidden>
  <symbol id="icon-chevron" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 25.228 14.029">
      <g transform="translate(1.414 1.414)">
          <path d="M0,11.2,11.2,0m0,22.4L0,11.2" transform="translate(0 11.2) rotate(-90)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"/>
      </g>
  </symbol>
</svg>

